Benue State Governor, Samuel Ortom has congratulated the General Overseer of the Redeemed Christian Church of God, RCCG, Pastor Enoch Adeboye on his 78th birthday. Ortom in a statement by his Chief Press Secretary, Terver Akase on Monday, described Pastor Adeboye as a true spiritual father whose selfless service and guidance in the Lordâ€™s vineyard have won millions of souls for God. He said Adeboye has demonstrated uncommon humility and the love of God through his teaching, preaching and lifestyle. He, therefore, prayed for sustained good health and strength to enable the renowned man of God do more for the church and humanity in general.